2026-05-31 14:27:59,589 - common.logger - INFO - 最终使用的 variables: {'shop_id': '71008738021cd3393bacbac182bd6a86af0b5c87'}
2026-05-31 14:27:59,590 - common.logger - INFO - 第一次替换后的请求参数: {'requestSource': 'businessNewOfListHeaderStatus'}
2026-05-31 14:27:59,590 - common.logger - INFO - 第一次替换后的 SQL: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT cobs.order_id) AS total_count
FROM llxz_order.ct_user_orders AS cuo
INNER JOIN llxz_order.ct_order_by_stages AS cobs ON cobs.order_id = cuo.order_id
WHERE cobs.statement_date BETWEEN CONCAT( CURDATE() + INTERVAL 1 DAY, ' 00:00:00' )
                              AND CONCAT( CURDATE() + INTERVAL 1 DAY, ' 23:59:59' )
  AND cobs.STATUS = 1
  AND cuo.STATUS IN ( '06', '07' )
  AND cuo.is_violation IN ( '01', '03' )
  AND cobs.shop_id = '71008738021cd3393bacbac182bd6a86af0b5c87'

